des:
Try A Moment for Success. By using this skill, you will find your stress levels decrease, and your confidence, creativity, and optimism elevate, as you become empowered to greater levels of personal achievement and better health.

This skill offers inspiring affirmations, vivid visualizations, 30-second brainstorming sessions, mindfulness practices, physical stretches designed to release block-causing mental stress, and more. 

Let 30 seconds make a difference for you!
